Submitter Information: Iris Diagnostics, a Division of IRIS International Inc.
Methodologies: Semi-automated urinalysis using urine chemistry test strips
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for iChem 100 Urine Chemistry Analyzer and iChem 10 SG strips for rapid, semi-automated urinalysis of multiple analytes via reflectance spectroscopy.
Indications for Use Summary: In vitro measurement of urine analytes (glucose, protein, bilirubin, urobilinogen, pH, specific gravity, blood, ketones, nitrite, leukocyte esterase, ascorbic acid, and color) in urine specimens using iChem 10 SG strips for evaluation of renal, urinary, and metabolic disorders by healthcare professionals.
